        How Does a Mortgage Discharge Work When Selling Your Brisbane Property?
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A mortgage discharge releases the lender's registered interest in your title at settlement. Here is exactly how it works, who handles it, and what sellers need to do.
      </p>
    </div>
